# Frontend Agent Rules

## Stack

Vanilla HTML/CSS/JS only. No frameworks, no build tools. Inline styles and scripts.

## Book Layout (participant.html)

- Left page = speaker's own words (`msg.side === "mine"`)
- Right page = other person's translation (`msg.side === "theirs"`)
- Visual moments (scene/sentiment) use `.visual-moment` class in right panel
- Debounce visual entries: 10s for scenes, 12s for sentiment

## Audio Pipeline

- Mic: `getUserMedia` → `AudioContext(16kHz)` → `ScriptProcessor(4096)` → Int16 PCM → `ws.send(buffer)`
- Playback: queue-based drain, rate-matched AudioContext (16kHz or 24kHz based on MIME)
- Never create new AudioContext per chunk — reuse `ctx16k`/`ctx24k`

## Camera + Motion Detection

- Camera PiP: `.cam-pip` container with `<video>` + `<canvas>` overlay
- Motion: 80x60 downsampled, 10px blocks, threshold 28, arrows at 300ms interval
- Frame capture for server: 320x240 JPEG at 3s interval via `captureFrame()`

## Color Palette

- Background: `#0e0e12`
- Warm accent: `rgba(191,155,120,...)`
- Active: green (#4caf50), Muted: red (#f44336), Camera: blue (#4a9eff)

## Polling

Billing: 15s interval. Never poll faster than 10s for any endpoint.
